'''拉加·索南·托杰·多吉'''（Raja Sonam Topgay Dorji，{{dz|d=སྟོབས་རྒྱས་རྡོ་རྗེ་|w=stobs-rgyas rdo-rje}}），{{bd|1896年||1953年}}），[[不丹|不丹]]政治人物，[[多吉家族|多吉家族]]成员。

== 生平 ==
索南·托杰·多吉是原[[不丹首相列表|不丹首席部长]][[乌颜·多吉|乌颜·多吉]]之子。1917年，他继其父出任首席部长之职<ref name=BFPG>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_EWuvGysPSIC |title=Bhutan Foreign Policy and Government Guide |volume=20 |series=World Foreign Policy and Government Library |author=Global Investment and Business Center, Inc. |publisher=Int'l Business Publications |pages=59–61 |year=2000 |isbn=0-7397-3719-8 |accessdate=2011-08-09 |archive-date=2013-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231200535/http://books.google.com/books?id=_EWuvGysPSIC |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并成为了不丹首任国王[[乌颜·旺楚克|乌颜·旺楚克]]的亲信之一。<ref>{{cite book |title=India and Bhutan |volume=1 |series=Studies in Asian History and Politics |first=Kapileshwar |last=Labh |publisher=Sindhu Publications |year=1974 |page=200 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sA4hAAAAMAAJ |accessdate=2011-08-12 |archive-date=2014-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704163900/http://books.google.com/books?id=sA4hAAAAMAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>不丹第二任国王[[吉格梅·旺楚克|吉格梅·旺楚克]]继任后，他继任担任首席部长。1953年9月，索南·托杰·多吉在[[印度|印度]][[噶伦堡|噶伦堡]]的不丹屋去世。<ref name=Royal>{{cite web |url=http://www.royalark.net/Bhutan/bhutan2.htm |title=BHUTAN – The Wangchuck Dynasty |date=2010-03-20 |first=Christopher |last=Buyers |work=The Royal Ark – Royal and Ruling Houses of Africa, Asia, Oceania and the Americas |accessdate=2011-08-10 |archive-date=2013-01-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DvaEDmvi?url=http://www.royalark.net/Bhutan/bhutan2.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=Sang />

